---
import { Icon } from "astro-iconify";

const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="mt-20 md:mt-36 mx-4">
  <div class="flex gap-4 border-b pb-8 mb-5 flex-col lg:flex-row">
    <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3">
      <h2 class="footer-title text-lg font-bold">都市大生スタッフ募集中！</h2>
      <p class="footer-paragraph text-sm">
        アニメーション制作に興味がある東京都市大学の学生を募集しています。詳しくはお問い合わせください。<br>
        経験は不問です。一緒に楽しくアニメーションを作りましょう！<br>
        <small>2024年12月まで募集しています。</small>
      </p>
	  <div class="flex gap-3 mt-3">
		<a href="mailto:g2172117@tcu.ac.jp" target="_blank" aria-label="メールを送る" />
			<Icon name="material-symbols:mail" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-500 dark:text-neutral-200" aria-hidden="true"/>
		</a>
		<a href="https://www.github.com/ManatoYamashita" target="_blank" aria-label="githubでコードを見る">
			<Icon name="radix-icons:github-logo" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-500 dark:text-neutral-200" aria-hidden="true"/>
		</a>
		<a href="https://www.instagram.com/manapuraza_com/" target="_blank"aria-label="Instagramをチェックする">
			<Icon name="radix-icons:instagram-logo" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-500 dark:text-neutral-200" aria-hidden="true"/>
		</a>
		
	  </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex lg:ml-auto gap-10 mt-1">
      <div>
        <h2 class="footer-title font-bold mb-3 text-base">
          Pages
        </h2>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a href="/blog" class="flex items-center gap-1 hover:no-underline hover:text-gray-600">Blog <Icon name="radix-icons:arrow-top-right" class="w-3 h-3" /></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/tags" class="flex items-center gap-1 hover:no-underline hover:text-gray-600">Tags <Icon name="radix-icons:arrow-top-right" class="w-3 h-3" /></a>
          </li>
			    <li>
				    <a href="/about" class="flex items-center gap-1 hover:no-underline hover:text-gray-600">About <Icon name="radix-icons:arrow-top-right" class="w-3 h-3" /></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="footer-title font-bold mb-3 text-base">
          Stakeholders
        </h2>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.tcu.ac.jp/" class="flex items-center gap-1 hover:no-underline hover:text-gray-600">東京都市大学 <Icon name="radix-icons:arrow-top-right" class="w-3 h-3" /></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.city.setagaya.lg.jp/" class="flex items-center gap-1 hover:no-underline hover:text-gray-600">東京都世田谷区 <Icon name="radix-icons:arrow-top-right" class="w-3 h-3" /></a>
          </li>
			    <li>
				    <a href="https://www.81produce.co.jp/" class="flex items-center gap-1 hover:no-underline hover:text-gray-600">81プロデュース <Icon name="radix-icons:arrow-top-right" class="w-3 h-3" /></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-sm font-medium mb-10">
    &copy; 2024-{today.getFullYear()} <a href="https://manapuraza.com" target="_blank"><strong>都市大アニメーション / ManatoYamashita</strong></a>&nbsp; All rights reserved.
  </p>
</footer>

<script>
  import { gsap } from 'gsap';
  import { ScrollTrigger } from 'gsap/ScrollTrigger';
  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

  gsap.from('.footer-title', {
    scrollTrigger: {
      trigger: 'footer',
      start: 'top 80%',
    },
    opacity: 0,
    x: -100,
    duration: 1,
    ease: 'power2.out',
  });

  gsap.from('.footer-paragraph', {
    scrollTrigger: {
      trigger: '.footer-paragraph',
      start: 'top 100%',
    },
    opacity: 0,
    y: 50,
    duration: 1,
    ease: 'power2.out',
  });
</script>